Source.Name: qt6-webengine
Source.Summary: QtWebEngine integrates chromium's fast moving web capabilities into Qt6
Source.Description: The Qt WebEngine module provides a web browser engine that makes it easy to embed content from the World Wide Web into your Qt application on platforms that do not have a native web engine.
